text: ... "Isn't this the madhouse you always wanted?" Lemur taunting.
... From Capitalism and Schizophrenia to Racism and Schizophrenia in one easy degeneration wave.
... Sailer's commentary is on every single point the non-psychotic take, and it just seems weird -- as if it comes from Mars, or something. ...
... The Sailer meta-narrative, that Western psychiatry has pretty much fully assimilated itself to psychosis at this stage, looks unassailable.
... If you want to know how lunatics think, ask a psychiatrist for their own most sincere opinions.
... Central task of Western psychiatry 2021: Contribute professional expertise to the maximum elaboration of paranoid-schizophrenic persecution fantasies.
... Model diagnosis: "Patient had the misfortune to be the Messiah and had been subsequently reincarnated both as Napoleon and Lenin, so his sense of persecution was clearly fully justified."
'Breathing' isn't instrumental enough. It's more: "The link between people not doing what I want -- especially giving me money -- and schizophrenia."

* Waves gun unsteadily, sweating profusely * 
"Hand over all your words!"
The coordination fiasco that is contemporary Western society in a nut shell. x.com/a_centrism/status/1414… ...
... That people can't sort things out better than this is so deeply pathetic it's almost comical.
